Start
/ events.add OnAsk binding on the input channel — verifies registration succeeds.
/ Driving an actual Ask through stdin is out of scope for an automated test;
/ this confirms the binding installs and the EventType + ChannelName plumb
/ through the catalog.
- on ask on "input" channel call CaptchaGoal, write to %bindingId%
- assert %bindingId% is not null
